Global Variable# kPDFDestinationUnspecifiedValue

iOS 11.0+iPadOS 11.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.4+tvOS 11.0+visionOS 1.0+

```
let kPDFDestinationUnspecifiedValue: CGFloat
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/PDFKit/kPDFDestinationUnspecifiedValue#Discussion)

Unspecified value used when a destination’s actual x or y value is unimportant.

## [See Also](/documentation/PDFKit/kPDFDestinationUnspecifiedValue#see-also)

### [Getting Pages and Points](/documentation/PDFKit/kPDFDestinationUnspecifiedValue#Getting-Pages-and-Points)

[`var page: PDFPage?`](/documentation/pdfkit/pdfdestination/page)Returns the page that the destination refers to.[`var point: CGPoint`](/documentation/pdfkit/pdfdestination/point)Returns the point, in page space, that the destination refers to.
